      "filePath": "strategies/README.md",
      "summary": "Strategies directory README in Chinese. Indexes the 10 canonical built-in strategies (ma_cross, expma_cross, macd_cross, bollinger_breakout, rsi_reversal, kdj_golden, turtle_breakout, bias_reversal, volume_price, obv_trend) by file, name, category, and applicable market regime, then shows a Strategy-subclass template for users to copy. Provides a usage pattern: `easy-tdx backtest SYMBOL --strategy-file strategies/<name>.py --table`.",
